stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> PENDING: token issued
    PENDING --> ACCEPTED: password setup succeeds
    PENDING --> REVOKED: admin resend
    PENDING --> REVOKED: Firebase fallback password setup
    PENDING --> REVOKED: employee archived/admin action
    PENDING --> EXPIRED: expiresAt elapsed
    ACCEPTED --> [*]
    REVOKED --> [*]
    EXPIRED --> REVOKED: admin resend supersedes historical invite
